      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Labbuns nahks/ bet paleê is-\nkaltuschâs Tuksnesês Weetâs/\nne-augliga Semmê/kur neweens\ndsihwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Swehtihts irr kas Zilweks/\nkas us to KUNGU vatanjahs/\nun ka Zerriba tas KUNGS ir-\nraid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Jo tas buhs ka weens\nKohks pee Uhdens dehstihts/ kas\nfawas Saknes istaisch pee Up-\npes/ un ne juht kad Karstume\nnahk/ winna Lappas paleê sat-\ntas/ un Bulla Gaddâ wiꞥsch\nne behda/ un ne mittejahs Aug-\ntus nest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Pahr wissahn Leetahm\nirr ta Sirde weena wiltiga/ un\nfamissufi (Leeta/) kas warr to\nismanniht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Es tas KUNGS isman-\n, nu to Sirde/ un pahrbandu tahs\nIbkstis/ un dohinu ikkatram\npehz faweem Zeffeem/ pehz teem\nAugteem fawn Darbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Jtt ka tas Putnis*/ kas\n(Pautus) debj/ bet ne isperre/\ntâvatt irr tas/ kas Baggatibu\nfakrahj/ bet ne ar Taifutbu/ fa-\nwas Dsihwibas Puusinehrâ\nbuhs winnam to atstaht/ un pa\nGallam weens Gekkis buht.\n* Eebr Wall: Kore.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Bet tas Krehslis tahs\nGohdibas/ kas no Eesahkuma\naugsts irraid/ irr muhsu jiveh-\nta Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Ak KUNGS! tu Isra-\netka Zerriba/ wiſti/ kas tewi at-\nstaht/ taps Kaunâ/ un manni\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Atkahpaji taps Semmê raksti-\nti/ jo tee atstahi to KUNGU/ ta\ndsihwa Uhdens Awoti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Dsredina manni / ak\nKUNGS! tad tapfchu es dsee-\ndinahts/ atpesti manni/ tad tap-\nfchu es atpestihts/ jo tu efi man-\nna teizama Slawa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Raugi/ tee fakka uhs\nmanni: Kur irr ta KUNGA\nWahrds: Laid jelle tas nahk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Tomehr es ne efmu spee-\ndeês/ ka es par Gannu buhtu /\ntew pakkat eet/ ir Zilweku Beh-\ndu Deenas es ne efmu eekahrojs/\ntu finni to: Kas no mannas\nMuttes irr tsqahjis/ tas irr ta-\nwa Dreekfcha (parei,i) bijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Ne tehpi tu man par\nIstruhzinaschanu: Tu efi mans\nPatwerums tauna Deenâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Laid manni Pakkatdsin-\nnejt Kauna tohp/ bet laid es ne\ntohpu Kaunâ/ lai tee istruhzina-\nti tohp/ bet laid es ne tohpu is-\ntruhzinahts/ Weddi pahr teem\nNelainibas Deenu/ un fatreez\ntohs ar diwkahrtign Satreek-\nschanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Ta irr tas KUNGS uhs\nmanni fazzijs: Efj/ un stahwi\nto Lauschu Wahrtis/ zaur ko\ntee sehnini no Juha ee-eet/ un\nzaur ko tee iseet/ ir wikas Je-\nrusalemes Wahrtis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Un fakki uhs teem: Klau-\nfajt ta KUNGA WahrdU/ juhs\nKehuiri no Juha / un wik\nJuha/ un wiki juhs Jerusa-\nlemes Eedsihwotaji/ kas juhs\n"
    }
  ],
